title: 226. NaNoWriMo - 30 November Update
itunes:author: Words and Nerds: Authors, books and literature.
itunes:summary: The NaNoWriMo Team of 2020 Adrian Beck, Tristan Bancks, Julianne Negri and Dani Vee, together with guests Fleur Ferris, Holden Sheppard and Sarah Bailey bring you the chaos that is NaNoWriMo from high expectations to self doubt, panic attacks, late night writing and outliers. be inspired, write along with us and join the conversation.
